          <msContents class="#STM">
            <summary><p>A copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Veṅkaikkōvai</title>, also known as <title xml:lang="ta">Mantirikkōvai</title>, by  <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Civappirakācatēvar</persName>, also known as <persName xml:lang="ta" role="author">Civappirakācar</persName>. See Zvelebil (1995, p. 177). 426 stanzas: 1 <foreign xml:lang="ta">kāppu</foreign> stanza + 425 stanzas.</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (January 2024).</p>

<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>    </summary>
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
            
